{"tid":1625923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣不是福建幫，是惠州幫的。","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:59:54.000Z","uid":330826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d257f62c653186864c613203f8df0e89e8c8d4","tid":1625923,"uid":330826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>荃灣各界將隆重慶祝國慶 籌委會成立 辦晚宴會操等11項活動  </strong><br />\n<br />\n  【香港商報訊】記者周駿報道：「荃灣各界慶祝國慶69週年籌委會成立大會」已於8月2日假荃灣悅來酒店舉行。今屆籌委會會長<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>鍾偉平、朱松勝，執行主席朱德榮</ins></span>，通過國慶聯歡晚宴、升旗禮暨大會操、國慶綜合文藝晚會等活動安排外，同場舉辦「國家改革開放40年香港的機遇和角色」講座，主講嘉賓為深圳培訓調研中心教研處副處長、副教授薛林博士。她首先講到1978年的十一屆三中全會，拉開了中國改革開放的大幕，改革開放40年，國家在經濟、科技、國防等方面取得了成就。薛林總結中國三代領導人治國大略時指出，毛澤東讓中國人民「站起來」，鄧小平則令人民「富起來」，而習近平則是走復興之路的「強起來」富國之路。 <br />\n<br />\n當晚，荃灣各界人士逾200人旁聽講座，<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣鄉委會副主席傅振光</span>發言稱，國家建設包括高架公路，當中最成功當數高鐵建設，而國家「一帶一路」關照沿途國家和地區，感受到國家建設力量的強大。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-08/13/content_1099105.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2018-08%2F13%2Fcontent_1099105.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=fcf7b587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-08/13/content_1099105.html</a><br />\n <br />\n___________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結論︰荃灣商會 請大家多愛國，多「感受到國家建設力量的強大」。</span><br />\n<br />\n以上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190316/photo/0316-00176-092b1.jpg?t=1570265777434\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190316%2Fphoto%2F0316-00176-092b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1570265777434&h=05f32065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣商會理事長：周鎮榮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190316/photo/0316-00176-092b2.jpg?t=1570265741308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190316%2Fphoto%2F0316-00176-092b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1570265741308&h=a0c14e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣商會監事長，廣東省惠州市政協常委︰朱德榮 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twta.com.hk/web/subpage.php?mid=16\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twta.com.hk%2Fweb%2Fsubpage.php%3Fmid%3D16&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2ce6eabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.twta.com.hk/web/subpage.php?mid=16</a>"},{"pid":"c7381d2cba90cab4b07c24fd1d05480c306444f0","tid":1625923,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以搵d共狗發泄"}]}